+modal('bip-dashboards', "Craft Dashboards")
  p Designed and prototyped a configurable dashboard framework for the Platform.
  p Widgets could be added, repositioned, and configured by users at runtime. Implemented a shared context system allowing widgets to subscribe to cross-widget state — such as a shared date range controlled by a toolbar widget.
  p Built a Risk Dashboard proof-of-concept that was demoed to enterprise clients and the product leadership team as a strategic initiative for the FY2022 roadmap.
